summary: The E-commerce Apparel Market is forecasted to soar to US$ 1.37 trillion by 2033 from US$ 685.72 billion in 2024, driven by an 8.07% CAGR between 2025 and 2033. Technological innovations, shifting consumer preferences, and increasing smartphone use fuel this growth.
